plots.title: Filesystem Capacity
plots.tsquery: select capacity_used, capacity_free where category = FILESYSTEM

plots.title: IO Utilization
plots.tsquery:
select read_ios_disk_min_rate, read_ios_disk_max_rate,
read_ios_disk_avg_rate, write_ios_disk_min_rate,
write_ios_disk_max_rate, write_ios_disk_avg_rate where category = CLUSTER
